Special Representative of the Chinese Government on Korean Peninsula Affairs Ambassador Liu Xiaoming traveled to Moscow on Saturday to meet with Russian officials, including the foreign minister and deputy foreign minister. Liu Xiaoming said on Twitter that the two sides had an in-depth discussion on the situation on the Korean Peninsula and international issues of common concern. (Cover image: Twitter post of Liu Xiaoming, Special Representative of the Chinese Government on Korean Peninsula Affairs Ambassador, March 26, 2022. / @AmbLiuXiaoMing)